description:
This is a 39 minute workout called '35 MIN PILATES WORKOUT || At-Home Mat Pilates (No Standing & No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
